title: Walton wins at Delhi under the lights; Eagles roll at Unatego
text:
Walton wins at Delhi under the lights; Eagles roll at Unatego 
By wbng sports October 3, 2015 Updated Oct 3, 2015 at 12:07 AM EDT 
Delhi, NY (WBNG Binghamton) For the first time since 1892, Walton and Delhi played a game at Delhi under the lights Friday night. The end result saw Walton (4-1) besting the Bulldogs (2-3), 22-6. 
Dawson Beers scored all three Walton touchdowns.
